ai.grakn.concept

Class ResourceType.DataType<D>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ai.grakn.concept.ResourceType.DataType<D>
  • Type Parameters:
    D - The data type.
    Enclosing interface:
    ResourceType<D>

    public static class ResourceType.DataType<D>
extends Object
    A class used to hold the supported data types of resources and any other concepts. This is used tp constrain value data types to only those we explicitly support.
